name: Pacman’s Return
overview: An AMOS freeware Pac-Man game clone by Anthony Brice, this was his second game ever after a Ping Pong game and the first version was created in about 38 days. With version 1.1 finished and released in August of 1993 according to his notes. 1.10 finished and uploaded to 17Bit Public Domain Library (disk number 2665) in September of 1994. In this version, when you eat a power-pill you can go much faster!
